name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Edgar GARCIA, Petitioner

parties: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Edgar GARCIA, Petitioner.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 29th day of January, 2009, the “Petition to Allow Nunc Pro Tunc Filing of a Petition for Allowance of Appeal from the Superior to the Supreme Court” is GRANTED. Counsel is directed to file a Petition for Allowance of Appeal within 15 days of the entry of our order.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.

casebody.head_matter:
COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Edgar GARCIA, Petitioner.
No. 173 EM 2008.
Supreme Court of Pennsylvania.
Jan. 29, 2009.
